Next, I checked the province resolutions, specifically 60-NQ/TW. I wanted to see if Gia Lai was listed for any province mergers. To confirm, I looked at the provided new ward list. I found "Xã Bờ Ngoong" there, with the code "23947" and province name "Tỉnh Gia Lai," matching my previous findings. This further confirms my initial reasoning.

Therefore, the output should be a JSON object with the ward name "Xã Bờ Ngoong," the province name "Tỉnh Gia Lai," and the ward code "23947." The citation will be from 1664/NQ-UBTVQH15, line 54, which states the direct merger. The confidence is high because of this specific mention.

I also considered whether other resolutions or new wards could be relevant, but given the provided data, I'm confident there is only one correct output.
